{"tid":1706484,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"美劇 CBS《Evil 邪惡異象》靈異現象 還是 科學巧合？","createTime":"2019-11-11T06:00:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T11:27:13.000Z","uid":250639,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cee983b3c71557c47e927f772c633f4f46181318","tid":1706484,"uid":250639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T06:00:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/adkx0HV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fadkx0HV.jpg&h=09f7c899&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美劇 CBS《Evil 邪惡異象》靈異現象 還是 科學巧合？<br />\nMichael Emerson將回歸CBS，主演正在開發的劇集。宅總飾演的角色叫湯森醫生，是個看上去非常和善、值得信任的人，是一起大屠殺案件的專家證人。但是，外表是具有欺騙性的，他很可能是一個邪惡的頭領，操控著一幫信徒執行可怕的謀殺計劃......正派男女主由Katja Herbers和Mike Colter扮演。這部劇是《傲骨賢妻》的Robert和Michelle King夫婦開發的<br />\n<br />\nCBS的新劇《Evil邪惡異象》EP01<br />\n女主角克里斯汀是心理學家<br />\n指證連環殺人犯奧森<br />\n其在犯案期間blacked out了的證供不可信<br />\n辯方卻突然提出他們的專家證人<br />\n湯森醫生 指出奧森他有齊惡靈附身的症狀<br />\n克里斯汀念出天主經 使奧森突然發狂施襲<br />\n然後克里斯汀聯同天主教教會調查人員<br />\n展開科學與靈異角度的調查<br />\n究竟奧森是瘋了還是得了精神病？<br />\n<br />\n連環殺人狂自稱鬼上身 是邪靈附身還是精神病?《邪惡異象》01<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1ZnOQHpLG5g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1ZnOQHpLG5g&d=30k2sE%2FAiGmcVOPaBnjdddHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=e964c53e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1ZnOQHpLG5g</a>"},{"pid":"1792638b4d0415261d977f2cb6e0c4de47fec657","tid":1706484,"uid":101756,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T06:20:44.000Z","msg":"你第日先推啦"},{"pid":"2adac2efcad5a94bbe52840a7c55a7d2a92774aa","tid":1706484,"uid":66893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1792638b4d0415261d977f2cb6e0c4de47fec657","tid":1706484,"uid":101756,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T06:20:44.000Z","msg":"你第日先推啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:27:13.000Z","msg":"Grace from Westworld<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇左頭兩集，好似麻麻，之後會唔會好返d？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gi